cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CY 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to recognize personality traits from text data in multiple languages. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a method for personality alignment, which involves mapping personality traits from one language to another, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also uses multilingual embeddings, which can be categorized under neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with cross-lingual transfer learning, which can be categorized under computational linguistics (cs.CY).
